function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	Hydra.QActorPlayEffectGroup(actor_MahjoobPerson, "actor_death_poison")

	Hydra.Wait(1.5)
	Hydra.ActorDelete(actor_MahjoobPerson)
	
	Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(spawn_MahjoobFly)

	--Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(idSelf, "MahjoobFly")
	
	local tFly = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("QST_Kehj_Infection_MahjoobFly")
	
	idMahjoob = tFly[1]

	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idMahjoob, false)
	Hydra.ActorSetTeam(idMahjoob, Hydra.TEAM_NEUTRAL)
	
	Hydra.Wait(1)
		
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(conv_MahjoobFly1, idMahjoob)

end
